    <div class="well" id="hamachi" >

        
        <a name="002194"></a>
        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://hamachi.cc/">Hamachi</a></h4>

        

        <p>To be tried-out:  Cross-platform app that creates VPNs between computers &#8212; even if they&#8217;re behind firewalls.  Downside: Requires connecting to a centrally-run server to initiate connection, which will soon be charging $$$.</p>

